item.title: Maribeth - Denpasar Moon
item.description:
Denpasar moon
shining on
An empty street
I return to the place
We used to meet
Denpasar moon
Shine your light
and let me see
That my love is still
waiting there for me-

I saw you
standing there
Through the rain I saw
you turn and smile
Were you
waving to me
Though the rain I ran
across the street
But you were gone
there was no one
You had vanished
with my dreams
Denpasar moon
shining on
An empty street
I return to the place
We used to meet
denpasar moon
Shine your light and
let me see
That my love is still
waiting there for me-

But you were gone
there was no one
You were gone
flying homeward
You were gone
there was no one
You had vanished
with my dreams
Denpasar moon
shining on
An empty street
I return to the place
We used to meet
denpasar moon
Shine your light and
let me see
That my love is still
waiting there for me
That my love is still
waiting there for me
Denpasar
moon-
